{"tid":1787424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「和理倒數」不如大家聖誕除夕齊齊出去老銅倒數，行街","createTime":"2019-12-18T02:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:50:58.000Z","uid":43785,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4cbbaa9df4fe117c0f2b48645bf41c7a55e7e9","tid":1787424,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"你地知唔知道？<br />\n2018就黎過了，讓我係度同你地講聲，聖誕快樂<br />\n但你地知唔知？<br />\n2019亦都就黎到，我想同你地講聲新年快樂。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，入番正題，<br />\n<br />\n政府日日鳩吹差過沙士，沙士時邊有人去食野，依家日日食飯要等位。股樓齊齊跌，有樓冇人買，有鋪冇人租。<br />\n政府似乎真係好驚呢件事會發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要經濟攬炒，似乎大家都不可以放軟手腳。<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n為左振興經濟帶旺消費<br />\n地鐵會開通宵方便人<br />\n既然係咁不如大家聖誕除夕唔好留係屋企了，<br />\n齊齊出去尖咀老銅倒數，<br />\n當晚一班人著黑衫既人一齊亂咁行街，行到夠鐘就倒數，除左感受一下節日氣氛外。更要高呼五大訴求。<br />\n但<span style=\"color: orange;\">由於市道氣氛變差，唔建議參與活動市民去商戶消費。純粹感受一下聖誕氣氛就好</span><br />\n和理SHOP威力加強版。聖誕攬炒經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於係普天同慶攬炒既日子，唔建議裝修，<br />\n不過兄弟爬山，你地裝我地都唔割，照支持。<br />\n<br />\n總之一齊happy new year<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊齊睇聖誕經濟攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n零售市道入寒冬，商戶叫業主地產商減租下年先有生意做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊齊炒爆經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6f27632803ee6136d70610853310d2c